01:20:33.140 --> 01:20:36.130
which is discussed in all
texts in quantum physics

01:20:36.130 --> 01:20:43.020
which says that the sum over
all oscillator strengths is 1.

01:20:43.020 --> 01:20:46.340
So, therefore, we know
if we have transitions

01:20:46.340 --> 01:20:49.220
from the ground state
to different states,

01:20:49.220 --> 01:20:52.000
the sum of all the oscillator
strengths to all the states

01:20:52.000 --> 01:20:53.508
can only be 1.

01:20:57.240 --> 01:21:02.830
And another advantage of the
